                                <img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/contentimages/arrow-orange.gif" /> <a href="/it/explore/itineraries/nsw-pacific-coast-touring-route.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43;">Pacific Coast Touring Route, Nuovo Galles del Sud</span></a><br />
